data.description: Look no further! This manicured home has it all! This home features 4 large bedrooms and 3 full baths. Large wooded back lot with privacy galore, trails in the back and a 6' privacy fenced in backyard.  Perfectly oversized in-law suite style bedroom on the main floor  with a full bathroom. The open concept floorplan from the abundantly cabinet  filled kitchen with Granite countertops is perfect for gatherings. New beautiful plank flooring on the main level with clean paint. This home has 3 bedrooms upstairs with a Media/bonus room. Plenty of room for the growing family! The large laundry room is upstairs with separate closets and plenty of space.  With plenty of parking space bring your camper or your boat!! You don't want to miss this one! 2 newer HVAC units installed within last two years!! Property eligible for 100% financing thru USDA
